    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 <i>Arctic Attire</i> 创作者包帅气地勇闯寒冷的遥远北方，此包与知名的<i>《Crusader Kings III》</i>模组作者 <i><strong>Aj</strong></i> 合作打造。<i>Arctic Attires</i> 加入灵感来自萨米与汗特美学的装饰物件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315550/extras/aad76796167819fff01cfc3b287d6250.poster.avif?t=1769779605\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315550/extras/aad76796167819fff01cfc3b287d6250.webm?t=1769779605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315550/extras/aad76796167819fff01cfc3b287d6250.mp4?t=1769779605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>此创作者包包含下列装饰物件：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 个服装风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 个腿部装备模型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 个斗篷</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 个头部装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 个护甲套装 (头部装备和护甲)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 个原声带，《Longing for the Land》(一种称为“joik”的萨米传统形式歌曲)</p></li></ul>",
